  "page": "Bethany",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Bethany</b> is a common female name in Westeros. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blushing_Bethany\" title=\"Blushing Bethany\">Blushing Bethany</a>, a prostitute at the Happy Port brothel in Braavos</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Fair-Fingers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bethany Fair-Fingers\">Bethany Fair-Fingers</a>, a musician scheduled to play at King Joffrey's wedding</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Blackwood\" title=\"Bethany Blackwood\">Bethany Blackwood</a>, the only daughter of Lord Tytos Blackwood</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Bracken\" title=\"Bethany Bracken\">Bethany Bracken</a>, a mistress of Aegon IV Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Hightower\" title=\"Bethany Hightower\">Bethany Hightower</a>, daughter of Lord Ormund Hightower.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Redwyne\" title=\"Bethany Redwyne\">Bethany Redwyne</a>, wed to Lord Mathis Rowan</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Rosby\" title=\"Bethany Rosby\">Bethany Rosby</a>, deceased sixth wife of Lord Walder Frey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Bolton\" title=\"Bethany Bolton\">Bethany Ryswell</a>, deceased second wife of Lord Roose Bolton</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bethany&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Beth_Cassel\" title=\"Beth Cassel\">Beth Cassel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Betha_Blackwood\" title=\"Betha Blackwood\">Betha Blackwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Betharios_of_Braavos\" title=\"Betharios of Braavos\">Betharios of Braavos</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 202604